{"text_id":210351,"tokens":["Op","posing"," the"," Policy"," of"," Allowing"," Cell"," Phones"," in"," School","\n\n","Cell"," phones"," have"," become"," an"," integral"," part"," of"," our"," lives",","," especially"," for"," teenagers","."," However",","," allowing"," students"," to"," bring"," and"," use"," their"," cell"," phones"," during"," school"," hours",","," but"," requiring"," them"," to"," turn"," them"," off"," during"," class"," time",","," is"," not"," an"," effective"," policy","."," While"," proponents"," argue"," that"," it"," offers"," benefits"," such"," as"," convenience"," and"," enhanced"," communication",","," the"," potential"," drawbacks"," outweigh"," these"," advantages",".","\n\n","One"," benefit"," often"," cited"," is"," the"," convenience"," factor","."," Allowing"," students"," to"," have"," their"," phones"," with"," them"," at"," all"," times"," means"," that"," they"," can"," use"," them"," before"," and"," after"," school"," hours"," for"," important"," communication"," or"," emergencies","."," However",","," this"," can"," easily"," be"," achieved"," by"," requiring"," students"," to"," leave"," their"," phones"," in"," their"," lockers"," or"," with"," the"," office"," during"," class"," time",","," ensuring"," they"," have"," access"," to"," them"," when"," necessary",".","\n\n","Another"," argument"," in"," favor"," of"," this"," policy"," is"," that"," it"," improves"," communication"," between"," students"," and"," their"," families","."," With"," cell"," phones",","," parents"," can"," easily"," reach"," their"," children"," to"," inform"," them"," about"," any"," changes"," in"," after","-","school"," plans"," or"," pick","-","up"," times","."," However",","," this"," can"," lead"," to"," distractions"," and"," disruptions"," during"," class"," time"," when"," students"," receive"," messages"," or"," calls"," from"," their"," parents","."," By"," turning"," off"," phones"," during"," class"," time",","," students"," can